Farah Manufacturing Co said itnamed Christopher Carameros senior vice president of finance,effective April 1.    Carameros will succeed Richard Jaeger as chief financialofficer. Jaeger, who continues as chief financial officer on atransitional basis, was named vice chairman responsible forcorporate finance.    Carameros has been in public accounting for 12 years, mostrecently as partner at Coopers and Lybrand. Reuter&#3;